sical electrodynamics. Finally it is shown how a line spectrum can\nappear at all in classical systems, as a counterpart of suitable stability\nproperties of the motions, with a broadening due to a coexistence of\nchaoticity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jul 2014 18:10:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-28"}
