ewood inequality and\nBohnenblust--Hille inequalities the same?\n  2) Are the optimal constants of the Hardy--Littlewood inequality independent\nof $p$ (at least for large $p$)?\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 26 Jul 2014 11:02:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Aug 2014 14:54:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-07"}
