 SL test in the future high-precision joint geometric constraints on dark\nenergy. The mock future supernova and baryon acoustic oscillation data are\nsimulated based on the space-based project JDEM. We find that the 30-yr\nobservation of SL test would help improve the measurement precision of\n$\\Omega_m$, $H_0$, and $w_a$ by more than 70\\%, 20\\%, and 60\\%, respectively,\nfor the $w_0w_a$CDM model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 26 Jul 2014 11:58:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Nov 2014 05:36:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-11"}
